      <p class="home-lede home-lede-greeting">Hi, I&rsquo;m Lee.</p>
      <p class="home-lede">I&rsquo;m an independent consultant. I&rsquo;m interested in <span class="home-place-note" tabindex="0" data-note="broadly: things you hold in your hand (hand tools, cameras, computers), and things you hold in your head (concepts, frameworks, protocols)">tools</span> and how we use them.</p>
      <section class="home-section home-history-section" aria-label="Background">
        <p class="home-history">Most of my work has been in and around public health and global health ethics, with formative detours through ecology and hospitality.</p>
        <p class="home-history">For a decade+ I&rsquo;ve worked to deliver on the promise of global health programs by better understanding and designing for the human capacities, potential, and interests our typical ways of working fail to reach.</p>
      </section>

